Seed plane for the Neck Connective

Source: R/data.R
mancneckseeds.Rd

These were generated by Chris Ordish of FlyEM and passed to Greg Jefferis on 18th April 2021 by Stuart Berg.

Usage

mancneckseeds

Format

An object of class data.frame with 3781 rows and 3 columns.

Details

Note that these positions are raw (8nm voxel) locations.

See also

mancsomapos

#> 2 20241 33939 67070
#> 3 19956 34014 67070
#> 4 20459 34021 67070
#> 5 20518 33991 67070
#> 6 21246 34029 67070
